        <mxCell id="h-oge6dWlyKnTTEBAcrw-2" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="flowchart TD &#xa; &#xa;A[User opens SPD Event App] --&gt; B{Choose user role} &#xa; &#xa;%% ========================= &#xa;%% CAREGIVER FLOW &#xa;%% ========================= &#xa; &#xa;B --&gt; C[Caregiver] &#xa; &#xa;C --&gt; C1{Does caregiver have an account?} &#xa; &#xa;C1 --&gt;|No| C2[Create Account] &#xa;C2 --&gt; C2A[Enter username, password, email, date of birth] &#xa;C2A --&gt; C2B[Account created successfully] &#xa;C2B --&gt; C3[Login] &#xa; &#xa;C1 --&gt;|Yes| C3[Login] &#xa; &#xa;C3 --&gt; C4{Login successful?} &#xa; &#xa;C4 --&gt;|No| C5[Forgot Password] &#xa;C5 --&gt; C5A[Enter email and username] &#xa;C5A --&gt; C5B[Reset password] &#xa;C5B --&gt; C3 &#xa; &#xa;C4 --&gt;|Yes| C6[Caregiver Home Page] &#xa; &#xa;C6 --&gt; C7[View available events] &#xa;C7 --&gt; C7A[Search or sort events by name/date] &#xa;C7A --&gt; C8{Select an event?} &#xa; &#xa;C8 --&gt;|No| C6 &#xa;C8 --&gt;|Yes| C9[View event details] &#xa;C9 --&gt; C9A[Reason: caregiver needs to know date, time, venue, event purpose, and suitability] &#xa; &#xa;C9A --&gt; C10{Register for event?} &#xa; &#xa;C10 --&gt;|No| C6 &#xa; &#xa;C10 --&gt;|Yes| C11[Fill in registration form] &#xa;C11 --&gt; C11A[Enter full name as per NRIC/FIN/Passport, contact, date of birth, email, and required event-specific questions] &#xa;C11A --&gt; C12{Are all compulsory fields filled?} &#xa; &#xa;C12 --&gt;|No| C13[Show error message] &#xa;C13 --&gt; C11 &#xa; &#xa;C12 --&gt;|Yes| C14{Duplicate registration?} &#xa; &#xa;C14 --&gt;|Yes| C15[Prevent duplicate registration] &#xa;C15 --&gt; C15A[Reason: avoids repeated attendance records and inaccurate reporting] &#xa;C15A --&gt; C6 &#xa; &#xa;C14 --&gt;|No| C16{Event capacity full?} &#xa; &#xa;C16 --&gt;|Yes| C17[Show event full message] &#xa;C17 --&gt; C17A[Reason: prevents overbooking] &#xa;C17A --&gt; C6 &#xa; &#xa;C16 --&gt;|No| C18[Submit registration] &#xa;C18 --&gt; C19[Registration confirmed] &#xa;C19 --&gt; C20[Caregiver receives confirmation and QR code] &#xa;C20 --&gt; C20A[Reason: gives proof of registration and prepares for faster check-in] &#xa; &#xa;C20 --&gt; C21[Event appears under Registered Events on home page] &#xa;C21 --&gt; C21A[Reason: caregiver can easily track events they actually registered for] &#xa; &#xa;C21 --&gt; C22{Before event} &#xa;C22 --&gt; C23[Receive notification reminder] &#xa;C23 --&gt; C23A[Reason: reduces forgotten attendance and improves turnout] &#xa; &#xa;C21 --&gt; C24{On event day} &#xa;C24 --&gt; C25[Caregiver checks in using QR code] &#xa;C25 --&gt; C26{Check-in successful?} &#xa; &#xa;C26 --&gt;|Yes| C27[Attendance marked as present] &#xa;C27 --&gt; C27A[Reason: attendance data becomes accurate for admin reporting] &#xa; &#xa;C26 --&gt;|No| C28[Submit issue to admin] &#xa;C28 --&gt; C28A[Example: late arrival, QR not working, attended but not recorded] &#xa;C28A --&gt; C29[Admin reviews and fixes attendance issue] &#xa; &#xa;C27 --&gt; C30{After event} &#xa;C30 --&gt; C31[Receive feedback reminder] &#xa;C31 --&gt; C32[Submit feedback form] &#xa;C32 --&gt; C32A[Rate satisfaction, usefulness, comments, suggestions] &#xa;C32A --&gt; C33[Feedback submitted successfully] &#xa;C33 --&gt; C33A[Reason: helps SPD understand whether the event was meaningful to caregivers and the disability community] &#xa; &#xa;C33 --&gt; C34[Feedback appears under Feedback Given] &#xa;C34 --&gt; C34A[Reason: caregiver can see real feedback history] &#xa; &#xa;C6 --&gt; C35[Customise app settings] &#xa;C35 --&gt; C35A[Change font size, colours, language, accessibility options] &#xa;C35A --&gt; C35B[Reason: supports caregivers with different digital literacy and accessibility needs] &#xa; &#xa;C6 --&gt; C36[Use AI Help Desk] &#xa;C36 --&gt; C36A[Reason: caregiver can get help if they are confused or face technical issues] &#xa; &#xa;C6 --&gt; C37[Contact Admin] &#xa;C37 --&gt; C37A[Reason: caregiver can report registration, attendance, or event-related problems directly] &#xa; &#xa;%% ========================= &#xa;%% ADMIN FLOW &#xa;%% ========================= &#xa; &#xa;B --&gt; D[Admin] &#xa; &#xa;D --&gt; D1[Admin Login] &#xa;D1 --&gt; D2{Login successful?} &#xa; &#xa;D2 --&gt;|No| D3[Forgot Password] &#xa;D3 --&gt; D3A[Enter email and username] &#xa;D3A --&gt; D3B[Reset password] &#xa;D3B --&gt; D1 &#xa; &#xa;D2 --&gt;|Yes| D4[Admin Dashboard] &#xa; &#xa;D4 --&gt; D5[Event Management] &#xa;D5 --&gt; D6{Admin task?} &#xa; &#xa;D6 --&gt;|Create event| D7[Create new event] &#xa;D7 --&gt; D7A[Enter title, date, time, venue, description, maximum capacity] &#xa;D7A --&gt; D7B[Add custom registration questions] &#xa;D7B --&gt; D7C[Choose whether questions are compulsory] &#xa;D7C --&gt; D7D[Publish event] &#xa;D7D --&gt; D7E[Reason: admin can customise each event based on different needs, such as children allowed or extra participant details] &#xa; &#xa;D6 --&gt;|Edit event| D8[Edit existing event] &#xa;D8 --&gt; D8A[Update event details, capacity, or questions] &#xa;D8A --&gt; D8B[Notify registered caregivers] &#xa;D8B --&gt; D8C[Reason: keeps participants updated if event details change] &#xa; &#xa;D6 --&gt;|Delete event| D9[Delete event] &#xa;D9 --&gt; D9A[Confirm deletion] &#xa;D9A --&gt; D9B[Notify affected caregivers] &#xa;D9B --&gt; D9C[Reason: prevents confusion and keeps records accurate] &#xa; &#xa;D4 --&gt; D10[Attendance Dashboard] &#xa;D10 --&gt; D11[View all registered participants] &#xa;D11 --&gt; D11A[Reason: replaces random dummy names with real registration data] &#xa; &#xa;D11 --&gt; D12[Search attendee by name] &#xa;D12 --&gt; D12A[Reason: admin can quickly find a participant during event check-in] &#xa; &#xa;D11 --&gt; D13[View total registrations] &#xa;D13 --&gt; D13A[Reason: admin can monitor event demand and capacity] &#xa; &#xa;D11 --&gt; D14{On event day} &#xa;D14 --&gt; D15[Take attendance] &#xa;D15 --&gt; D16{Check-in method} &#xa; &#xa;D16 --&gt;|QR scan| D17[Scan caregiver QR code] &#xa;D17 --&gt; D17A[Mark participant as present] &#xa;D17A --&gt; D17B[Reason: faster and more accurate than manual checking] &#xa; &#xa;D16 --&gt;|Manual check-in| D18[Search participant name] &#xa;D18 --&gt; D18A[Mark participant as present manually] &#xa;D18A --&gt; D18B[Reason: backup method if QR code fails] &#xa; &#xa;D15 --&gt; D19[Attendance status updated] &#xa;D19 --&gt; D19A[Reason: admin can produce accurate attendance reports for SPD] &#xa; &#xa;D4 --&gt; D20[Feedback Dashboard] &#xa;D20 --&gt; D21[View all submitted feedback] &#xa;D21 --&gt; D22[Filter feedback by event] &#xa;D22 --&gt; D23[View average ratings] &#xa;D23 --&gt; D24[Read comments and suggestions] &#xa;D24 --&gt; D24A[Reason: admin can evaluate whether events are useful and meaningful] &#xa; &#xa;D20 --&gt; D25{Use AI sentiment analysis?} &#xa;D25 --&gt;|Yes| D26[AI summarises positive, neutral, and negative comments] &#xa;D26 --&gt; D26A[Reason: saves admin time when reviewing many responses] &#xa; &#xa;D25 --&gt;|No| D27[Admin reviews feedback manually] &#xa; &#xa;D4 --&gt; D28[Export Reports] &#xa;D28 --&gt; D29[Export attendance records to CSV/Excel] &#xa;D29 --&gt; D30[Export feedback report] &#xa;D30 --&gt; D31[Draft or send report email] &#xa;D31 --&gt; D31A[Reason: reduces manual reporting workload] &#xa; &#xa;D4 --&gt; D32[Capacity Monitoring] &#xa;D32 --&gt; D33[View remaining slots] &#xa;D33 --&gt; D34{Capacity reached?} &#xa; &#xa;D34 --&gt;|Yes| D35[Close registration automatically] &#xa;D35 --&gt; D35A[Reason: prevents overbooking] &#xa; &#xa;D34 --&gt;|No| D36[Continue accepting registrations] &#xa; &#xa;D4 --&gt; D37[Notification Centre] &#xa;D37 --&gt; D38[Send announcements or reminders] &#xa;D38 --&gt; D38A[Reason: informs caregivers about upcoming events, schedule changes, or feedback forms] &#xa; &#xa;D4 --&gt; D39[Direct Communication / Ticketing] &#xa;D39 --&gt; D40[View caregiver issues] &#xa;D40 --&gt; D41{Issue type} &#xa; &#xa;D41 --&gt;|Attendance issue| D42[Verify registration and update attendance] &#xa;D42 --&gt; D42A[Reason: fixes cases where caregiver attended but was not logged] &#xa; &#xa;D41 --&gt;|Registration issue| D43[Check form details and registration status] &#xa;D43 --&gt; D43A[Reason: helps caregivers who face form or confirmation problems] &#xa; &#xa;D41 --&gt;|General question| D44[Reply to caregiver] &#xa;D44 --&gt; D44A[Reason: provides support without relying only on WhatsApp] &#xa; &#xa;D4 --&gt; D45[AI Help Desk] &#xa;D45 --&gt; D45A[Reason: admin can troubleshoot app issues faster] &#xa; &#xa;D4 --&gt; D46[Third-party Communication Integration] &#xa;D46 --&gt; D46A[WhatsApp, Telegram, Facebook, Discord] &#xa;D46A --&gt; D46B[Reason: allows faster information sharing through familiar platforms]" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="3180" width="560" x="10" y="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="bmrPLBeBm0jQ17y7nl1M-2" parent="1" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="60" width="120" x="790" y="-30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <UserObject label="" mermaidData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;flowchart TD\n  A[User opens SPD Event App] --&gt; B{Choose user role}\n  \n  B --&gt; C[Caregiver]\n  C --&gt; C1{Does caregiver have an account?}\n  C1 --&gt;|No| C2[Create Account]\n  C2 --&gt; C2A[Enter username, password, email, date of birth]\n  C2A --&gt; C2B[Account created successfully]\n  C2B --&gt; C3[Login]\n  C1 --&gt;|Yes| C3\n  C3 --&gt; C4{Login successful?}\n  C4 --&gt;|No| C5[Forgot Password]\n  C5 --&gt; C5A[Enter email and username]\n  C5A --&gt; C5B[Reset password]\n  C5B --&gt; C3\n  C4 --&gt;|Yes| C6[Caregiver Home Page]\n  C6 --&gt; C7[View available events]\n  C7 --&gt; C7A[Search or sort events by name/date]\n  C7A --&gt; C8{Select an event?}\n  C8 --&gt;|No| C6\n  C8 --&gt;|Yes| C9[View event details]\n  C9 --&gt; C9A[Confirm date, time, venue, purpose, suitability]\n  C9A --&gt; C10{Register for event?}\n  C10 --&gt;|No| C6\n  C10 --&gt;|Yes| C11[Fill in registration form]\n  C11 --&gt; C11A[Enter name, contact, DOB, email, event-specific questions]\n  C11A --&gt; C12{All compulsory fields filled?}\n  C12 --&gt;|No| C13[Show error message]\n  C13 --&gt; C11\n  C12 --&gt;|Yes| C14{Duplicate registration?}\n  C14 --&gt;|Yes| C15[Prevent duplicate registration]\n  C14 --&gt;|No| C16{Event capacity full?}\n  C16 --&gt;|Yes| C17[Show event full message]\n  C16 --&gt;|No| C18[Submit registration]\n  C18 --&gt; C19[Registration confirmed]\n  C19 --&gt; C20[Receive confirmation and QR code]\n  C20 --&gt; C21[Event appears under Registered Events]\n  C21 --&gt; C22{Before event}\n  C22 --&gt; C23[Receive notification reminder]\n  C21 --&gt; C24{On event day}\n  C24 --&gt; C25[Check in using QR code]\n  C25 --&gt; C26{Check-in successful?}\n  C26 --&gt;|Yes| C27[Attendance marked as present]\n  C26 --&gt;|No| C28[Submit issue to admin]\n  C28 --&gt; C29[Admin reviews and fixes attendance]\n  C27 --&gt; C30{After event}\n  C30 --&gt; C31[Receive feedback reminder]\n  C31 --&gt; C32[Submit feedback form]\n  C32 --&gt; C32A[Rate satisfaction, usefulness, comments]\n  C32A --&gt; C33[Feedback submitted successfully]\n  C33 --&gt; C34[Feedback appears under Feedback Given]\n  C6 --&gt; C35[Customise app settings]\n  C35 --&gt; C35A[Change font size, colours, language, accessibility]\n  C6 --&gt; C36[Use AI Help Desk]\n  C6 --&gt; C37[Contact Admin]\n  \n  B --&gt; D[Admin]\n  D --&gt; D1[Admin Login]\n  D1 --&gt; D2{Login successful?}\n  D2 --&gt;|No| D3[Forgot Password]\n  D3 --&gt; D3A[Enter email and username]\n  D3A --&gt; D3B[Reset password]\n  D3B --&gt; D1\n  D2 --&gt;|Yes| D4[Admin Dashboard]\n  D4 --&gt; D5[Event Management]\n  D5 --&gt; D6{Admin task?}\n  D6 --&gt;|Create| D7[Create new event]\n  D7 --&gt; D7A[Enter title, date, time, venue, description, capacity]\n  D7A --&gt; D7B[Add custom registration questions]\n  D7B --&gt; D7C[Choose if questions compulsory]\n  D7C --&gt; D7D[Publish event]\n  D6 --&gt;|Edit| D8[Edit existing event]\n  D8 --&gt; D8A[Update event details, capacity, or questions]\n  D8A --&gt; D8B[Notify registered caregivers]\n  D6 --&gt;|Delete| D9[Delete event]\n  D9 --&gt; D9A[Confirm deletion]\n  D9A --&gt; D9B[Notify affected caregivers]\n  D4 --&gt; D10[Attendance Dashboard]\n  D10 --&gt; D11[View all registered participants]\n  D11 --&gt; D12[Search attendee by name]\n  D12 --&gt; D13[View total registrations]\n  D13 --&gt; D14{On event day}\n  D14 --&gt; D15[Take attendance]\n  D15 --&gt; D16{Check-in method}\n  D16 --&gt;|QR scan| D17[Scan caregiver QR code]\n  D17 --&gt; D17A[Mark participant as present]\n  D16 --&gt;|Manual| D18[Search participant name]\n  D18 --&gt; D18A[Mark participant as present manually]\n  D17A --&gt; D19[Attendance status updated]\n  D18A --&gt; D19\n  D4 --&gt; D20[Feedback Dashboard]\n  D20 --&gt; D21[View all submitted feedback]\n  D21 --&gt; D22[Filter feedback by event]\n  D22 --&gt; D23[View average ratings]\n  D23 --&gt; D24[Read comments and suggestions]\n  D24 --&gt; D25{Use AI sentiment analysis?}\n  D25 --&gt;|Yes| D26[AI summarises comments]\n  D25 --&gt;|No| D27[Admin reviews feedback manually]\n  D4 --&gt; D28[Export Reports]\n  D28 --&gt; D29[Export attendance records to CSV/Excel]\n  D29 --&gt; D30[Export feedback report]\n  D30 --&gt; D31[Draft or send report email]\n  D4 --&gt; D32[Capacity Monitoring]\n  D32 --&gt; D33[View remaining slots]\n  D33 --&gt; D34{Capacity reached?}\n  D34 --&gt;|Yes| D35[Close registration automatically]\n  D34 --&gt;|No| D36[Continue accepting registrations]\n  D4 --&gt; D37[Notification Centre]\n  D37 --&gt; D38[Send announcements or reminders]\n  D4 --&gt; D39[Direct Communication / Ticketing]\n  D39 --&gt; D40[View caregiver issues]\n  D40 --&gt; D41{Issue type}\n  D41 --&gt;|Attendance| D42[Verify registration and update attendance]\n  D41 --&gt;|Registration| D43[Check form details and status]\n  D41 --&gt;|General| D44[Reply to caregiver]\n  D4 --&gt; D45[AI Help Desk]\n  D4 --&gt; D46[Third-party Communication Integration]\n  D46 --&gt; D46A[WhatsApp, Telegram, Facebook, Discord]&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;config&quot;: null&#xa;}" id="bmrPLBeBm0jQ17y7nl1M-3">
